": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"the past few months\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On April 5, for example, an arrest warrant was issued against former Bihar Chief Minister and Rashtriya Janata Dal Chief Lalu Prasad Yadav in a case related to the alleged illegal purchase of arms and ammunition in 1995-97.\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4040, \"end\": 4045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bihar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 2.8285049531684057e-11, \"text\": \"Bihar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bihar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bihar\"}, {\"begin\": 4065, \"end\": 4085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rashtriya_Janata_Dal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rashtriya Janata Dal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rashtriya_Janata_Dal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rashtriya_Janata_Dal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"an arrest warrant\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4119}, {\"ngram\": \"the alleged illegal purchase\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4159}, {\"ngram\": \"arms\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4167}, {\"ngram\": \"ammunition\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is clear that investigating agencies of the government are trying to imprison, or merely entangle in legal troubles, leading opposition figures so that they are not able to devote full attention and energy to their election campaigns.\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"agencies\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4253}, {\"ngram\": \"legal troubles\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4314}, {\"ngram\": \"full attention\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4393}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4404}, {\"ngram\": \"their election campaigns\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government appears also to be targeting opposition institutions to limit their ability to run an effective election campaign.\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4449}, {\"ngram\": \"opposition institutions\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"their ability\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"an effective election campaign\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past month, India's Income Tax Department served the main opposition Congress Party multiple tax notices worth hundreds of millions of dollars and recovered 1.35 billion rupees ($16.32m) in penalties from its bank accounts.\", \"from\": 4566, \"to\": 4798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4587, \"end\": 4592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 4595, \"end\": 4616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.442853229115228e-25, \"text\": \"Income Tax Department\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 4644, \"end\": 4658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past month\", \"from\": 4571, \"to\": 4585}, {\"ngram\": \"dollars\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4717}, {\"ngram\": \"1.35 billion rupees\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"its bank accounts\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also sealed the party's bank accounts, leaving it with limited access to funds just weeks prior to the elections.\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the party's bank accounts\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4839}, {\"ngram\": \"limited access\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"funds\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"the elections\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Congress Party said they view the actions of the Income Tax Department as an effort to damage the party's campaigning efforts, and thus as an attack on Indian democracy.\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 5089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4920, \"end\": 4934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 4969, \"end\": 4990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.442853229115228e-25, \"text\": \"Income Tax Department\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 5072, \"end\": 5078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the actions\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4961}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"the party's campaigning efforts\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"an attack\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On April 1, the Income Tax Department told the Supreme Court that it would not pursue a 35-billion rupee ($420 million) payment from the Congress Party until after the completion of general elections in June, giving the opposition some breathing space.\", \"from\": 5091, \"to\": 5343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5107, \"end\": 5128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.442853229115228e-25, \"text\": \"Income Tax Department\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 5138, \"end\": 5151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5775912277790286e-35, \"text\": \"Supreme Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 5228, \"end\": 5242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5099}, {\"ngram\": \"a 35-billion rupee ($420 million) payment\", \"from\": 5177, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"the completion\", \"from\": 5255, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"general elections\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposition\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5321}, {\"ngram\": \"some breathing space\", \"from\": 5322, \"to\": 5342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet the tax payments are not the only tools utilised by the government against opposition institutions and actors.\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tax payments\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5364}, {\"ngram\": \"the only tools\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5387}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5414}, {\"ngram\": \"opposition institutions\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5446}, {\"ngram\": \"actors\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day, there is news of one or the other leader or prominent figure of some opposition party joining the BJP.\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5569, \"end\": 5572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 5480, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"the other leader\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5511}, {\"ngram\": \"prominent figure\", \"from\": 5515, \"to\": 5531}, {\"ngram\": \"some opposition party\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is widely believed that these opposition figures are leaving their parties and joining the governing BJP as a result of intimidation and harassment from the government's investigative agencies.\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5678, \"end\": 5681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these opposition figures\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5625}, {\"ngram\": \"their parties\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5651}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 5685, \"to\": 5693}, {\"ngram\": \"intimidation\", \"from\": 5697, \"to\": 5709}, {\"ngram\": \"harassment\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5724}, {\"ngram\": \"the government's investigative agencies\", \"from\": 5730, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2019, former Maharashtra Chief Minister and Congress leader Ashok Chavan gave an interview to the Hindustan Times, alleging \\\"BJP is using government agencies to threaten leaders in opposition\\\".\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5788, \"end\": 5799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\", \"score\": 0.9890295120482413, \"rank\": 0.011092174518217828, \"text\": \"Maharashtra\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharashtra\"}, {\"begin\": 5819, \"end\": 5827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9999999596284405, \"rank\": 4.037200758135915e-08, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 5835, \"end\": 5847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashok_Chavan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ashok Chavan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashok_Chavan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashok_Chavan\"}, {\"begin\": 5873, \"end\": 5888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hindustan Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\"}, {\"begin\": 5900, \"end\": 5903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 5853, \"to\": 5865}, {\"ngram\": \"government agencies\", \"from\": 5913, \"to\": 5932}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5952}, {\"ngram\": \"opposition\", \"from\": 5956, \"to\": 5966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our leaders were threatened with inquiries,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5970, \"to\": 6024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our leaders\", \"from\": 5971, \"to\": 5982}, {\"ngram\": \"inquiries\", \"from\": 6004, \"to\": 6013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Agencies such as the Enforcement Directorate and Income Tax were used to initiate action against institutions run by them.\", \"from\": 6025, \"to\": 6148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6047, \"end\": 6070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enforcement_Directorate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Enforcement Directorate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enforcement_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enforcement_Directorate\"}, {\"begin\": 6075, \"end\": 6085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.788399557050181e-25, \"text\": \"Income Tax\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Income_Tax_Department\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Agencies\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6034}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 6108, \"to\": 6114}, {\"ngram\": \"institutions\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then they were assured protection from action if they joined the ruling parties.\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"protection\", \"from\": 6172, \"to\": 6182}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6194}, {\"ngram\": \"the ruling parties\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who joined them were scared of action against them.\", \"from\": 6230, \"to\": 6287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 6267, \"to\": 6273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ones who did not budge are still on the radar.\\\"\", \"from\": 6288, \"to\": 6339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ones\", \"from\": 6288, \"to\": 6296}, {\"ngram\": \"the radar\", \"from\": 6328, \"to\": 6337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, Chavan himself has been threatened by BJP leaders with prosecution and incarceration.\", \"from\": 6341, \"to\": 6438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6391, \"end\": 6394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chavan\", \"from\": 6353, \"to\": 6359}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecution\", \"from\": 6408, \"to\": 6419}, {\"ngram\": \"incarceration\", \"from\": 6424, \"to\": 6437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He left Congress and joined BJP in February 2024.\", \"from\": 6439, \"to\": 6488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6447, \"end\": 6455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9999999596284405, \"rank\": 4.037200758135915e-08, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 6467, \"end\": 6470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 6474, \"to\": 6482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this month, the Indian Express published an investigation into opposition figures who crossed over to the BJP.\", \"from\": 6490, \"to\": 6608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6514, \"end\": 6520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 6604, \"end\": 6607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 6539, \"to\": 6555}, {\"ngram\": \"opposition figures\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The journalists examined the cases of 25 opposition leaders facing corruption charges who left their parties and joined the BJP since 2014.\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6733, \"end\": 6736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The journalists\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6624}, {\"ngram\": \"the cases\", \"from\": 6634, \"to\": 6643}, {\"ngram\": \"25 opposition leaders\", \"from\": 6647, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption charges\", \"from\": 6676, \"to\": 6694}, {\"ngram\": \"their parties\", \"from\": 6704, \"to\": 6717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They found that 23 of them got reprieves - three cases were closed and 20 were stalled, or put in \\\"cold storage\\\", meaning no action is being taken against the accused.\", \"from\": 6749, \"to\": 6916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reprieves\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6789}, {\"ngram\": \"three cases\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6803}, {\"ngram\": \"cold storage\", \"from\": 6848, \"to\": 6860}, {\"ngram\": \"no action\", \"from\": 6871, \"to\": 6880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"India's opposition parties are being hollowed out with such tactics.\", \"from\": 6918, \"to\": 6986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6918, \"end\": 6923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such tactics\", \"from\": 6973, \"to\": 6985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Further, such actions are causing the public to lose faith in the opposition and perceive opposition parties as institutions that are in disarray, filled with people crippled with fear and unfit to govern.\", \"from\": 6987, \"to\": 7192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such actions\", \"from\": 6996, \"to\": 7008}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 7021, \"to\": 7031}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 7040, \"to\": 7045}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposition\", \"from\": 7049, \"to\": 7063}, {\"ngram\": \"perceive opposition parties\", \"from\": 7068, \"to\": 7095}, {\"ngram\": \"institutions\", \"from\": 7099, \"to\": 7111}, {\"ngram\": \"disarray\", \"from\": 7124, \"to\": 7132}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7146, \"to\": 7152}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 7167, \"to\": 7171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indian media also plays an important role in giving the BJP an advantage in the election.\", \"from\": 7194, \"to\": 7283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7194, \"end\": 7200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 7250, \"end\": 7253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important role\", \"from\": 7218, \"to\": 7235}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 7254, \"to\": 7266}, {\"ngram\": \"the election\", \"from\": 7270, \"to\": 7282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, most of the Indian media is openly promoting BJP and Narendra Modi.\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7305, \"end\": 7311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 7338, \"end\": 7341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 7346, \"end\": 7359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the announcement of elections, media platforms have been organising events featuring the prime minister and other ministers and BJP leaders, giving them every opportunity to promote themselves and their agenda.\", \"from\": 7361, \"to\": 7577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7495, \"end\": 7498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 7367, \"to\": 7383}, {\"ngram\": \"elections\", \"from\": 7387, \"to\": 7396}, {\"ngram\": \"media platforms\", \"from\": 7398, \"to\": 7413}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 7435, \"to\": 7441}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime minister\", \"from\": 7452, \"to\": 7470}, {\"ngram\": \"other ministers\", \"from\": 7475, \"to\": 7490}, {\"ngram\": \"every opportunity\", \"from\": 7520, \"to\": 7537}, {\"ngram\": \"their agenda\", \"from\": 7564, \"to\": 7576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This courtesy has not been extended to opposition leaders.\", \"from\": 7578, \"to\": 7636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This courtesy\", \"from\": 7578, \"to\": 7591}, {\"ngram\": \"opposition leaders\", \"from\": 7617, \"to\": 7635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Media has also been pushing the narrative that the opposition is weak, the PM remains popular and there is no real alternative to him or the BJP.\", \"from\": 7637, \"to\": 7782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7778, \"end\": 7781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Media\", \"from\": 7637, \"to\": 7642}, {\"ngram\": \"the narrative\", \"from\": 7665, \"to\": 7678}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposition\", \"from\": 7684, \"to\": 7698}, {\"ngram\": \"the PM\", \"from\": 7708, \"to\": 7714}, {\"ngram\": \"no real alternative\", \"from\": 7744, \"to\": 7763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any independent media organisation or new media platform that dares to move away from the government narratives is facing attacks and intimidation from the government.\", \"from\": 7784, \"to\": 7951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any independent media organisation\", \"from\": 7784, \"to\": 7818}, {\"ngram\": \"new media platform\", \"from\": 7822, \"to\": 7840}, {\"ngram\": \"the government narratives\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7895}, {\"ngram\": \"attacks\", \"from\": 7906, \"to\": 7913}, {\"ngram\": \"intimidation\", \"from\": 7918, \"to\": 7930}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 7936, \"to\": 7950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many popular YouTube channels critical of the government have been given notices or already shut down.\", \"from\": 7952, \"to\": 8054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many popular YouTube channels\", \"from\": 7952, \"to\": 7981}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 7994, \"to\": 8008}, {\"ngram\": \"notices\", \"from\": 8025, \"to\": 8032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The communal rhetoric used by the BJP and the prime minister in the run-up to the election has also harmed the democratic process.\", \"from\": 8056, \"to\": 8186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8090, \"end\": 8093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The communal rhetoric\", \"from\": 8056, \"to\": 8077}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime minister\", \"from\": 8098, \"to\": 8116}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 8120, \"to\": 8130}, {\"ngram\": \"the election\", \"from\": 8134, \"to\": 8146}, {\"ngram\": \"the democratic process\", \"from\": 8163, \"to\": 8185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the very first day of the election campaign, BJP campaigners including the prime minister have started using communal language.\", \"from\": 8188, \"to\": 8320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8238, \"end\": 8241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the very first day\", \"from\": 8193, \"to\": 8211}, {\"ngram\": \"the election campaign\", \"from\": 8215, \"to\": 8236}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime minister\", \"from\": 8264, \"to\": 8282}, {\"ngram\": \"communal language\", \"from\": 8302, \"to\": 8319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PM Modi attacked the Congress Party by saying that every page of its election manifesto \\\"bears the imprint of the Muslim League\\\".\", \"from\": 8321, \"to\": 8450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8342, \"end\": 8356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 8435, \"end\": 8448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-India_Muslim_League\", \"score\": 0.999999998621206, \"rank\": 1.3761489267476735e-09, \"text\": \"Muslim League\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-India_Muslim_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-India_Muslim_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr