democracy?\", \"from\": 8806, \"to\": 8899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8882, \"end\": 8888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their actions\", \"from\": 8827, \"to\": 8840}, {\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 8869, \"to\": 8878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one really expects the Election Commission, appointed by the prime minister himself, to do anything.\", \"from\": 8900, \"to\": 9003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8926, \"end\": 8945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.401261587964783e-33, \"text\": \"Election Commission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 8900, \"to\": 8906}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime minister\", \"from\": 8960, \"to\": 8978}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 8994, \"to\": 9002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The international community is watching all this with concern.\", \"from\": 9005, \"to\": 9067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The international community\", \"from\": 9005, \"to\": 9032}, {\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 9059, \"to\": 9066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time in the history of independent India that the representative of the secretary-general of the United Nations has considered it necessary to make a statement that in India \\\"people's political and civil rights\\\" are \\\"protected\\\" and everyone can vote in a \\\"free and fair\\\" atmosphere.\", \"from\": 9068, \"to\": 9368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9121, \"end\": 9126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 9183, \"end\": 9197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.014615125386736e-16, \"text\": \"United Nations\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 9254, \"end\": 9259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 9076, \"to\": 9090}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 9094, \"to\": 9105}, {\"ngram\": \"the representative\", \"from\": 9132, \"to\": 9150}, {\"ngram\": \"the secretary\", \"from\": 9154, \"to\": 9167}, {\"ngram\": \"general\", \"from\": 9168, \"to\": 9175}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 9234, \"to\": 9245}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"people's political and civil rights\", \"from\": 9260, \"to\": 9296}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 9318, \"to\": 9326}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"free and fair\\\" atmosphere\", \"from\": 9339, \"to\": 9367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the way Indian state institutions are currently functioning, one can only hope the UN statement proves accurate when the polls open later this month.\", \"from\": 9369, \"to\": 9524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9383, \"end\": 9389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 9458, \"end\": 9460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9999999544434114, \"rank\": 4.555641519213159e-08, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 9375, \"to\": 9382}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 9436, \"to\": 9439}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 9492, \"to\": 9501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The upcoming election is very important for the future of democracy in India.\", \"from\": 9526, \"to\": 9603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9597, \"end\": 9602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The upcoming election\", \"from\": 9526, \"to\": 9547}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 9570, \"to\": 9580}, {\"ngram\": \"democracy\", \"from\": 9584, \"to\": 9593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is clear that all the constitutional institutions in the country have now decided that they are working for the BJP, not the people, and the media has taken up the role of the current government's propagandist.\", \"from\": 9604, \"to\": 9817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9719, \"end\": 9722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023104274256286e-20, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the constitutional institutions\", \"from\": 9621, \"to\": 9656}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 9660, \"to\": 9671}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 9728, \"to\": 9738}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 9744, \"to\": 9753}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 9767, \"to\": 9775}, {\"ngram\": \"the current government's propagandist\", \"from\": 9779, \"to\": 9816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hands and feet of the opposition parties are tied.\", \"from\": 9818, \"to\": 9872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hands\", \"from\": 9818, \"to\": 9827}, {\"ngram\": \"feet\", \"from\": 9832, \"to\": 9836}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposition parties\", \"from\": 9840, \"to\": 9862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In such a situation, the only hope is that the Indian people, who fought relentlessly for democracy since the country's inception and know its worth very well, will understand the seriousness of the situation, and use their strongest weapons, their votes, to put an end to India's rapid democratic backsliding.\", \"from\": 9873, \"to\": 10183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9920, \"end\": 9933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999743422453, \"rank\": 2.5658052543858607e-08, \"text\": \"Indian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 10146, \"end\": 10151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997762688758, \"rank\": 2.0253208686723336e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a situation\", \"from\": 9876, \"to\": 9892}, {\"ngram\": \"the only hope\", \"from\": 9894, \"to\": 9907}, {\"ngram\": \"democracy\", \"from\": 9963, \"to\": 9972}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's inception\", \"from\": 9979, \"to\": 10002}, {\"ngram\": \"its worth\", \"from\": 10012, \"to\": 10021}, {\"ngram\": \"the seriousness\", \"from\": 10049, \"to\": 10064}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 10068, \"to\": 10081}, {\"ngram\": \"their strongest weapons\", \"from\": 10091, \"to\": 10114}, {\"ngram\": \"their votes\", \"from\": 10116, \"to\": 10127}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 10136, \"to\": 10142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If not, the upcoming Indian elections will go down in history as a farcical play put on only to please, placate and provide renewed legitimacy to Modi and his party, not much different from Dictator Aladeen's Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 10185, \"to\": 10408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10206, \"end\": 10212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998529801922, \"rank\": 1.4702020397148546e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 10331, \"end\": 10335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8171190221269527e-71, \"text\": \"Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 10239, \"to\": 10246}, {\"ngram\": \"a farcical play\", \"from\": 10250, \"to\": 10265}, {\"ngram\": \"renewed legitimacy\", \"from\": 10309, \"to\": 10327}, {\"ngram\": \"his party\", \"from\": 10340, \"to\": 10349}, {\"ngram\": \"Dictator Aladeen's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 10375, \"to\": 10407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The views expressed in this article are the author's own and do not necessarily reflect Al Jazeera's editorial stance.\", \"from\": 10410, \"to\": 10528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10498, \"end\": 10508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.581232416890024e-14, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], 